'''天光'''（{{Lang-sa|स्वरभानु}} Svarabhānu ) <ref name="Stella" />是印度教[[阿修罗_(印度神话)|阿修罗]]，传统上在[[吠陀宗教|吠陀神话中]]代表[[日食|日食]]。这个名字也被用作[[往世书|往世书]]中[[罗睺|罗睺]]和[[計都|計都]]的属性，<ref name="Stella" />他们也与[[日食|日食]]和[[月食|月食]]有关。
== 神话 ==
[[File:BritishmuseumRahu.JPG|缩略图]]
阿修罗天光在《[[梨俱吠陀|梨俱吠陀]]》中被两次描述。<ref name="Hale">{{Cite book|last=Wash Edward Hale|title=Ásura- in early Vedic religion|pages=63–6|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=wN6dz2UZkw4C&dq=svarbhanu&pg=PA63|isbn=978-81-208-0061-8|year=1986|publisher=Motilal Banarsidass}}</ref>天光袭击太阳神[[蘇利耶|蘇利耶]]，用黑暗笼罩太阳。<ref>[https://books.google.com/books?id=phGzVwTTp_gC&pg=PA258&lpg=PA258&dq=Svarbhanu+Purana&source=bl&ots=tUAljfztRd&sig=RiJw2tqJBAH9hLqWqQTZNP8fqHk&hl=en&ei=jFQBS9SUEMXenAeTtOiXCw&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=12&ved=0CDYQ6AEwCw#v=onepage&q=Svarbhanu%20Purana&f=false Mitchiner 1982, p. 258]</ref>{{Le|斯特拉·克拉姆里奇|Stella Kramrisch}}以此将其视为天光比太阳更伟大的神。<ref name="Stella">{{Cite book|last=Kramrisch|first=Stella|last2=Burnier|first2=Raymond|title=The Hindu temple|volume=2|pages=325–6|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=8-aS52MgIkMC&dq=svarbhanu&pg=PA325|isbn=978-81-208-0224-7|year=1976|publisher=Motilal Banarsidass Publ.}}</ref>梨俱吠陀在此之后再次叙述，[[因陀羅|因陀罗]]击败了天光，[[阿低利|阿低利]]仙人找到了隐藏的太阳并在天空中取而代之。<ref name="Hale" /><ref name="Antonio" /> 天光还出现在《[[夜柔吠陀|夜柔吠陀]]》和[[梵书|梵书]]中。 <ref name="Hale" />根据梵书的说法，天光用黑暗刺穿了太阳，然而又被众神通过{{Le|svara|svara}}释放了。<ref>''Jaiminīya Brāhmaṇa'' 2:386; ''Maitrāyaṇi Brāhmaṇa'' 4:5:2</ref>

作为{{Le|蘇揭羅|Shukra}}（太白仙人）的助手，天光也是阿修罗的老师。他通过欺骗手段喝到了{{Le|摩醯尼|Mohini}}提供的[[甘露_(长生不老药)|甘露]]，尽管随后被斩首,但获得了两个不朽的生命体，他的头是罗睺，身体是計都。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.scribd.com/doc/259992/9-Ketu-and-Its-Forms |title=Chander 2000, p. 2 |access-date=2022-04-20 |archive-date=2009-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090203115403/http://www.scribd.com/doc/259992/9-Ketu-and-Its-Forms }}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|last=B S Shylaja, H R Madhusudan|title=Eclipse|pages=2|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=OQo37jub5TcC&dq=Swarbhanu&pg=PA2|isbn=978-81-7371-237-1|year=1999|publisher=Universities Press}}</ref>

根据《[[摩诃婆罗多|摩诃婆罗多]]》，太阳神[[蘇利耶|蘇利耶]]也被描述为“天光之敌”。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.booksboost.com/K/Kisari_Mohan_Ganguli_(Translator)/The_Mahabharata_of_Krishna_Dwaipayana_Vyasa/read_page16.html |title="Sambhava" parvan, Section LXVII |access-date=2022-04-20 |archive-date=2012-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120301061802/http://www.booksboost.com/K/Kisari_Mohan_Ganguli_(Translator)/The_Mahabharata_of_Krishna_Dwaipayana_Vyasa/read_page16.html }}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|last=Johannes Adrianus Bernardus van Buitenen|title=The Mahabharata|volume=2|pages=242, 784|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=YNZFdBgP2ZEC&dq=svarbhanu&pg=PA782|isbn=978-0-226-84664-4|year=1981|publisher=[[University_of_Chicago_Press|University of Chicago Press]]}}</ref>据说天光用箭射穿日月，又如《梨俱吠陀》中描写的同样日月被[[阿低利|阿低利]]复原。<ref name="Antonio">{{Cite book|last=Antonio Rigopoulos|title=Dattātreya: the immortal guru, yogin, and avatāra|pages=3–4}}</ref>

根据《{{Le|诃利世系|Harivamsa}}》，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mahabharata-resources.org/harivamsa/hv_1_47.html |title=1:47:52 |access-date=2022-04-20 |archive-date=2022-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220118235359/http://mahabharata-resources.org/harivamsa/hv_1_47.html }}</ref>天光带领罗刹{{Le|迦罗尼弥|Kalanemi}}穿过银河。根据《往世书》中描述，天光为辛悉迦的儿子。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cyberastro.com/articles/article_kaal_sarpa1.asp |title=Kāla-Sarpa Yoga |access-date=2022-04-20 |archive-date=2015-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151021233855/http://www.cyberastro.com/articles/article_kaal_sarpa1.asp }}</ref>

